Subject: My Top 6 Wealth Building Lessons (Plus a Bonus)
Snippet: Hey, Have you noticed? Every second day for the past 2 weeks I've released a new video. There's some pretty cool stuff in there. Along with personal stories of my own journey, I've got
Message_body:
[

Hey, Have you noticed? Every second day for the past 2 weeks I've released a new video. There's some pretty cool stuff in there. Along with personal stories of my own journey, I've got awesome interviews, research into what makes successful people tick, along with some funny high production value stuff. I even hired out a whole bar for one of the videos, and had the staff from the Lurn office act in it. It's not going to win an Emmy, but I think you'll get a laugh :) Below is a link to each of the videos. They're all pretty short, if there's any you've missed, you should watch it now... The One Thing 88% of Wealthy People do Every Day [https://track.slsv2.com/track/click/E6q0TJ3QFD/a9ad954558f87de089578deb701ab3d4/07208c78925d76b23a2053c95395a638/inbox16 From Military to 7 Figure Entrepreneur [https://track.slsv2.com/track/click/E6q0TJ3QFD/a9ad954558f87de089578deb701ab3d4/cddd061be603ed4d06a9957f704e3d73/inbox16 My Own Personal Dream Board [https://track.slsv2.com/track/click/E6q0TJ3QFD/a9ad954558f87de089578deb701ab3d4/051317fce63b9048cee6e89541ee293c/inbox16 #1 Business Lesson From a Drunk Man in a Bar (Very Funny) [https://track.slsv2.com/track/click/E6q0TJ3QFD/a9ad954558f87de089578deb701ab3d4/d331d8ce76c2af8605d2f210d2e3ea54/inbox16 The 9 Things I do Every Morning To Set My Day Up For Success [https://track.slsv2.com/track/click/E6q0TJ3QFD/a9ad954558f87de089578deb701ab3d4/b6576b6d9eee96c4c1b51d3e34b53dfd/inbox16 My Journey: How I Went From $1.7 Million In Debt To 8 Figure Business [https://track.slsv2.com/track/click/E6q0TJ3QFD/a9ad954558f87de089578deb701ab3d4/a019e2671a5a572607589fe61d9ae3d1/inbox16 And last of all, it's not a video, but make sure you do the eSCORE quiz, and discover what your personal strengths are, and what you need to work on to become a successful entrepreneur. Subject: before I turned 30..
Snippet: Hey, Business wise, I'm doing pretty well. My company will do over $20 million this year, I have an amazing team spread across half a dozen different countries, I've got an AMAZING office... no
Message_body:
[

Hey, Business wise, I'm doing pretty well. My company will do over $20 million this year, I have an amazing team spread across half a dozen different countries, I've got an AMAZING office... no... facility, which includes a 200 person lecture hall, 3 connected classrooms, offices, meeting rooms... etc. But I hasn't been smooth sailing to get here! Did you know, that by the time I reached 30 years old, I had build a multi million dollar empire, lost it all, fell $1.7 million in debt, paid back that debt, then built it all back up to an 8 figure business! I made a video of my journey, watch it now [https://track.slsv2.com/track/click/pyrKw2En6J/51a97c48de1d345aedef8b23fb7d2fa0/a019e2671a5a572607589fe61d9ae3d1/inbox16 And that was all before I hit 30!! I don't want to toot my own horn, but can you imagine the things I must have learned through these experiences? What if you could just grab the key important lessons from all this, and just download them to your brain. How powerful would that be! Well... you can! I've taken all of this information, all of the learning I've had through building massive empires, losing it all, crushing debt, and building again...
